SELECT [t1].[Exp_Name] AS [ExpName], [t1].[Exp_Desc] AS [ExpDesc], [t1].[Exp_Company] AS [ExpCompany], [t1].[Exp_In_Prog] AS [ExpInProg], [t1].[Exp_Sdate] AS [ExpSdate], [t1].[Exp_Edate] AS [ExpEdate], [t5].[Skill_Name] AS [SkillName], [t4].[Domain_Name] AS [DomainName], [t2].[Country_Name] AS [CountryName], [t3].[Region_Name] AS [RegionName]
FROM [TM_CND_Candidate] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [TR_HEX_Have_Experience] AS [t0] ON [t].[Candidate_Code] = [t0].[Candidate_Code]

INNER JOIN [TM_USR_User_Account] AS [t0] ON [t].[User_Code] = [t0].[User_Code]
WHERE [t].[Candidate_Adress] = @__mail_0
